public enum ClientCommandMode
extends java.lang.Enum<ClientCommandMode>

Defines the types of the FRI client commands.

NO_COMMAND_MODE -> No command mode available
JOINT_POSITION -> Commanding joint positions by the client
WRENCH -> Commanding joint positions and wrenches by the client
